#HEADER_START
/*
 * Seychelles for TTL 5.
 * Edited by T-West, December 2025.
 *
 * Based on the map by Deathcounter used for the LingYuan Cup and
 * Thalassocracy Cup 2.
 */

/* The original comments follow. */
/*
Title: Seychelles

Description:
Their villages located on the connected main lands of the archipelagic state of
the Seychelles, players will have to choose which body of water they want to
control. The inner sea that has more plentiful fish, or the outside waters that
provide better access to the enemy but also opens itself up to the the resource
and oyster-rich islands.

Created and submitted by Deathcounter for Blue Carbon Cup 2 B-Tier (chosen)

Submitted to Warlord 4 (Water category) S-Tier - 3rd place (not chosen)
Submitted to LingYuan Cup

Start Date: 17.10.24
Finished: 25.10.24

Suitable Player count: 1v1, 2v2
Currently supported modes: RM, Regicide, QS

Updated to 1v1 alongside improvements
26.03.25 - 28.03.25

Updated to allow QS (9 Vill)
11.07.25
*/
#HEADER_END

/*
 * Defeat players if the game mode is not set to random map.
 * Includes a check for the secondary game mode checkboxes.
 */
if ANTIQUITY_MODE
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
elseif RANDOM_MAP
  if REGICIDE
    #define ADMIN_RESTART
  elseif EMPIRE_WARS
    #define ADMIN_RESTART
  elseif SUDDEN_DEATH
    #define ADMIN_RESTART
  endif
else
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
endif
if TINY_MAP
else
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
endif
if DEFAULT_RESOURCES
else
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
endif
if DARK_AGE_START
else
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
endif
if TURBO_MODE
  #define ADMIN_RESTART
endif
if ADMIN_RESTART
  <PLAYER_SETUP>
  guard_state SABOTEUR AMOUNT_GOLD 0 1
endif


