/*

Actor Areas Number = [Description](Radius)

Playerowned
actorarea 1 = MAIN GOLD (5)
actorarea 2 = MAIN STONE (5)
actorarea 3 = BERRIES (3)
actorarea 4 = WATERBUILDING (0)
actorarea 5 = BOX TURTLES next berries(8)
actorarea 6 = ONGRID to place (1)
actorarea 7 = WATERBUILDING which turns into(0)
actorarea 8 = 3 BOX TURTLES (4)
actorarea 9 = FISHING HELPER (2)
actorarea 10= SECONDARY GOLDS(3)
actorarea 11= MIDDLE FISH HELPER (2)
actorarea 12= SNAPPER (6)
actorarea 13= DORADO (6)
actorarea 14= OYSTERS (6)
actorarea 15= YURT (5)
actorarea 16= TUNA for rare DOLPHIN (11)
actorarea 17= HUGE BEACH ROCKS for better distribution (20)
actorarea 18= HUGE BEACH ROCKS (20)
actorarea 19= STONE on Desert (5)
actorarea 20= Extra Bushes to make Forests nicer (5)
actorarea 21= QS Bush Straggler
actorarea 22= Box Turtles in middle (1)
actorarea 23= Main Island shore Box Turtles (5)
/* Idk why I put GAIA objects in the player owned list */

GAIA
actorarea 100 = Neutral Island Stone (2)
actorarea 101 = Neutral Island Gold (2)
actorarea 102 = Mangrove on Beach (20)
createactorarea 103 = RELIC North (45)
createactorarea 104 = RELIC E (45)
createactorarea 105 = RELIC S (45)
createactorarea 106 = RELIC W (45)

Perimeters
Not needed, too few lands to justify


*/


