/*
 * T-West: Keep player forests away from side forests.
 * Note that because of the default loose grouping, the trees do not fill the
 * entire 7x7 square defined by the group placement radius of 3. This creates a
 * good bit of randomness in the forest sizes and shapes.
 */
/* Player Forests */
